msgid "Auto-capture Virtual Orders"
msgstr "Auto-innen virtuele bestellingen"

#: src/Gateways/PayPal/PayPal_Settings.php:230
msgid "When using \"Authorize & Capture Later\" mode, automatically capture orders containing only virtual or downloadable products."
msgstr "Wanneer je \"Autoriseren en later innen\"-modus gebruikt, automatisch innen van bestellingen die alleen virtuele of downloadbare producten bevatten."

#: src/Gateways/PayPal/PayPal_Settings.php:236
msgid "Alternative Payment Methods"
msgstr "Alternatieve betaalmethoden"

#: src/Gateways/PayPal/PayPal_Settings.php:237
msgid "Toggles for alternative payment methods funded by PayPal PPCP that do not have a dedicated settings page. Google Pay, Apple Pay, Card, Fastlane and Pay Later are configured on their own settings pages."
msgstr "Schakelaars voor alternatieve betaalmethoden die via PayPal PPCP worden gefinancierd en geen eigen instellingenpagina hebben. Google Pay, Apple Pay, Kaart, Fastlane en Pay Later worden op hun eigen instellingenpagina’s geconfigureerd."

