msgid "Surface-by-surface control of the Pay Later messaging block. PayPal recommends rendering messaging on the product, cart, and checkout pages so eligible buyers see financing options before they commit."
msgstr "Per-oppervlakte-controle van het Pay Later-berichtenblok. PayPal raadt aan om berichten te renderen op de product-, winkelwagen- en afrekenpagina’s zodat geschikte kopers financieringsopties zien voordat ze zich verbinden."

#: src/Gateways/PayPal/PayPal_Settings.php:261
msgid "Show Pay Later messaging on individual product pages (PayPal recommended)."
msgstr "Toon Pay Later-bericht op individuele productpagina’s (Aanbevolen door PayPal)."

#: src/Gateways/PayPal/PayPal_Settings.php:268
msgid "Show Pay Later messaging on the cart page (PayPal recommended)."
msgstr "Toon Pay Later-bericht op de winkelwagenpagina (Aanbevolen door PayPal)."

#: src/Gateways/PayPal/PayPal_Settings.php:274
msgid "Side Cart (Drawer)"
msgstr "Zijwinkelwagen (Lade)"

